Description: Comprehensive academic workflow automation suite
 The Academic Workflow Suite provides tools and utilities for researchers,
 students, and academics to manage their work more efficiently.
 .
 Features include:
  - Research paper organization and management
  - Citation and bibliography tools
  - Collaboration utilities
  - Data analysis helpers
  - Integration with academic databases
